e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"呢個陳雲屌過，舊時d人專注讀完畢業搞掂<br />\n家陣直頭要你十項全能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8e6d9efd56778941b517c87f2ab7643e09127d","tid":435481,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個陳雲屌過，舊時d人專注讀完畢業搞掂<br />\n家陣直頭要你十項全能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下d HR就知，又要gpa高，又要有比賽活動相關經驗，又要有intern，non-related嘅intern扣你分，最好畢業前考埋cfa<br />\n<br />\n人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba778fc7ae40579bc385bccc6a4cd8ab47f11222","tid":435481,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>義大利經濟呢幾年都係咁差<br />\n無廉價勞工啲公司遲早執粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但意大利啲嘢賣好貴喎，啲皮鞋閒閒地五千蚊一對，意大利皮具真係世界number 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻啦<br />\n義大利人用普通牌子啲料都係一樣<br />\n但價錢平大半<br />\n係啲傻仔先會仆去買佢啲名牌啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de931c2df8b1b2b053b51294bb33a6807aa50c92","tid":435481,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"今年做某國際出版公司有$7000一個月，朝9晚5，真係唔覺做奴隸，反正可以寫靚cv"}]}